📋 DESCRIPTION
S7-based infrastructure for fitting mediation models,
extracting path coefficients, and bootstrap inference.
Foundation package for mediationverse ecosystem.

Version: 0.2.1 CRAN resubmission pending (branch feature/cran-round2); dev at 0.3.0; origin/main at 0.3.0. feature/fit-weights carries 0.3.1 (no PR yet).

