  references (MacKinnon, Lockwood & Williams 2004; Tofighi & MacKinnon 2011) as
  `<doi:...>`; added `\value` to the four exported print methods; converted
  `\dontrun{}`→`\donttest{}` (self-contained, lavaan guarded); bumped to **0.2.1**.
- ✅ **Hardening** — strict `_R_CHECK_SUGGESTS_ONLY_` + `--run-donttest` caught
  the default parametric bootstrap hard-requiring **MASS** (a Suggests pkg) →
  moved **MASS to Imports**. `--as-cran --run-donttest` + DEPENDS_ONLY/SUGGESTS_ONLY
  = **0/0/0**.
- ✅ **win-builder R-devel (0.2.1)** = 1 NOTE (author surnames only; noted in cran-comments).
- ✅ **Forward-ported** all fixes + MASS→Imports to `dev` (0.3.0); added a
  **noSuggests CI job** to `R-CMD-check.yaml` (CI all green). Enriched
  `inst/CITATION` with method references + ORCID. rforge proposal written
  (`docs/specs/PROPOSAL-cran-incoming-hardening-2026-06-10.md`).
- 🎯 **NEXT:** resubmit `medfit_0.2.1.tar.gz` + confirm email → then the cascade.

